name: Warehouse (sandwitsh)
description:
warehouse is a game about getting a key while avoiding enemies. this is my second project and im very proud of it. (note: if you download, windows might say this is a virus, i dont think it is)

controls:

F - fullscreen

R - change tip

SPACE - teleport (dont use it on walls. i dont know how to make it so that you cant teleport in walls)

wasd - move
